Blackfang grins. There was his chance.

Blackfang: And go where Kup? Out of the base? All right, I'm going...

He jumps off and down on the floor, then springs at Kup with enough 
strength to throw him on the ground.

--- In nbwrpg@y..., RoboRick007 <rfa007@c...> wrote:
> : : Kup / Rodimus Prime : :
> 
> The realization dawns on Prime and Kup. They lower their weapons.
> 
> Kup: You set off every alarm in the ship and damn near gave me a 
heart attack.
> 
> Rodimus Prime: Well if this is all under control....
> 
> Kup: Just go already.
> 
> Rodimus is out of the room in the blurr. He walks towards his 
quarters.
